# Audits & Reports

!!!abstract
    This folder hosts the project's **`audits`**, which consist of both the scripts needed to perform them and the reports they produce. In the case when the projects consists of multiple subprojects, this folder's internal structure is likely to be partionned in a way that reflects the relationships between those subprojects. This folder's content may also have content that it shares with the [/resources/useful-tools/](/resources/useful-tools/.gitkeep) folder.
